summary: I'M SO FUCKING MAD RIGHT NOW!!!! How COULD KEVIN FEIGH DO THIS!!!?? Wwhats the point even of this show. I'M STILL GONNA WATCH IT...
question: I'M SO FUCKING MAD RIGHT NOW!!!! How COULD KEVIN FEIGH DO THIS!!!?? Wwhats the point even of this show. I'M STILL GONNA WATCH IT Anyway. I just thought ..😭😭😭 i saw your post and I Just flipped. its nice of u to say dat maybe Loki might appear in phase 4 but wit no character growth. But tbh, wats d point even. He doesn't heal, he never finds peace. WHats the point?!  Its pretty obvious though dat there's no Loki in phase 4. That's it. I might as well accept it. I'm sorry I'm just so mad😭😭
answer:
We be sad together anon 😖😖😖

I could only see two interpretations to what Kevin Feigh said, and Loki doesn’t get any character growth and development or any kind of change to him (that is actually very clear. There’s no other way to look at it) in his series, and also he won’t be part of the future of the MCU (this part you can kinda say ‘maybe he won’t’ but still the fact that he was talking about the other series leaves me feeling major doubt).

You know I’m just not hoping any more. I’m just like you anon. Might as well face the facts. Kevin Feigh didn’t even mince words but the major entertainment sites though intelligently changed the wording.

summary: One of the videos on youtube complaining about The Unstoppable Wasp has in the title "statistically improbable ethnically...
body:
One of the videos on youtube complaining about The Unstoppable Wasp has in the title “statistically improbable ethnically ambiguous lesbians”

I’m sorry? Do you think lesbians are mythical in some way? Buddy, I got news they’re actually quite common.  Not nearly the cryptids you make them out to be.

Also ethnically ambiguous how? Have you just never seen a black person before?  What the fuck does that even mean?

Why can’t I find coverage of this comic by people who have been outside before?
